videos.description: Trent Dilfer breaks down the importance of TE Rob Gronkowski being on the field for the Patriots, saying "There's six eyes on Gronk on every play. That means there's six eyes that aren't on somebody else."
videos.headline: Dilfer: Gronk's presence a major factor in Patriots' success
